    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The gas limit in the genesis block is just the \"starting\" limit, that can move up or down by 1/1024th every block, which is up to your miner to control. By default the target gas limits shipped with Geth is 4.7M. You can change this via the `--targetgaslimit` option (just set whatever you want your gas limit to stay at).",
